<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="12.0pt;10.0pt"><font face>Bema
Dirava dekenai oiemu abidadama oi habadaia, inai gau namodia danu do idia
habadaia emu mauri lalonai. </span>Bema oi
be hari sibona inai Lauma Helaga ena dala oi davaria, inai gau namodia sedira do
oi abia haraga lasi. </span>To oi hesiku
lasi. </span>Bema oi abidadama henia noho
neganai inai gau namodia do oi davaria, Ekalesia gunadia idia davaria bamona.</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="12.0pt;10.0pt"><font face>Badina
dahaka Keristen (Ekalesia) taudia momo be inai mauri namona idia diba lasi?</font></span></p>
    <p align="center">
    </p>
    <div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%" background="images/spirback.gif">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><font face><font size="6"><span style=" 10.0pt;       ">2</span></font><span style=" 12.0pt;  10.0pt;       ">. <b style>SIBONA
          IDIA LALOA EKALESIA TAUDIA BE MAURI NAMONA MOMOKANI IDIA ABIA DIBA
          LASI.</b></span></font></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div><p align="left"><b><font size="3" face><span style="      ">Sibona
ia laloa tauna be ia laloa sibona ena goada dekenai Keristen o Ekalesia dalana
do ia raka:-</span></font></b> </p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="12.0pt;10.0pt"><font face>A.
Inai bamona tauna be sedira Dirava ena lalokau bona siahu ia diba lasi.
</span>O sedira nega ta ia kamonai, to ia laloaboio vadaeni.
</span><b><font color="#1413AB">(Roma 5: 8-10, Heberu 10: 1-25, 1 Ioane 1: 1-10,
1 Ioane 2: 1-2, 2 Petero 1: 9, Aposetolo edia Kara
</span>1:8.)</font></b></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="12.0pt;10.0pt"><font face>B.
Ena mauri be mai moale momokani lasi.</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="12.0pt;10.0pt"><font face>C.
Ia ura kara namodia karaia, to ia hegeregere lasi.</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font face><span style="12.0pt;10.0pt">D.
Lauma Helaga ese ia ura unai tau ia hasiahua gwauraia, vadaeni mauri namona do
ia abia. </span>To unai tau ena abidadama
ia henia lasi dainai, Lauma Helaga ese siahu ia henia lasi.
</span></span><b><span style=" 12.0pt;  10.0pt;       "><font color="#1413AB">(1 Korinto 3: 1-3, Roma
7: 15-24, Roma 8:7, Galatia 5: 16-18.)</font></span></b></font></p>
    <p><font face><br>
    <font size="3"><b><span style="font-family:        ">SIBONA
    IA LALOA TAUNA</span> <span style="12.0pt;10.0pt;
font-family:&quot;;&quot;;
">Inai
    bamona kara idia vara Dirava idia abidadama henia lasi tandia edia mauri
    lalonai:</span></b></font> <br>
    </font>
    </p>
<div align="center">
    <table border="0" width="90%" cellpadding="4">
      <tr>
        <td valign="middle" align="left"><b><font color="#1413AB" face><span style=" 12.0pt;  10.0pt;       ">Lauma
          Helaga ia karaia gaudia be momo, to unai tau ia diba lasi inai gaudia.
          </span>Ia be Dirava ia kamonai henia lasi.
          </span>Ia be Dirava ia lalokau henia lasi, idau taudia danu ia lalokau
          henia lasi. </span>Buka Helaga
          ia ura lasi duahia.</span></font></b></td>
        <td valign="middle" align="center">
